            <p>Welcome to Movie Ratings! We provide a platform for movie enthusiasts to discover, rate, and review their favorite movies.</p>
            <p>Whether you're a casual moviegoer or a hardcore cinephile, you'll find something to enjoy on Movie Ratings.</p>
            <p>Explore our extensive database of movies, read reviews from other users, and share your own ratings and thoughts.</p>
